ct class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"title":"MLNShape"}}}